  "original_title": "CAKE launches the #TakeCare Initiative",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "CAKE launches the #TakeCare Initiative",
      "author": "Thilina Walpola",
      "body_lines": [
        "CAKE Engineering, a Mad Mobile Company, is delighted to announce the launch of the #TakeCare Initiative, a community outreach project which focuses on supporting selected programmes to uplift underprivileged communities across Sri Lanka.",
        "Commenting on the launch, Branding and Communications Lead, Nishan de Silva Wijeyeratne, said, \u201cthe #TakeCare Initiative is an embodiment of our Mad Mobile values and is one of our ways of reimagining the future by providing vulnerable communities with much needed support. This programme will include social work that aligns with the organization\u2019s overall mission and help support sustainable development goals, while being funded by donations from the Group\u2019s global operations, individual donations, and fundraising activities by the employees of CAKE Engineering.\u201d",
        "To mark the launch of the #TakeCare Initiative, the organization donated a month\u2019s worth of dry rations to low-income earning families affected by the economic crisis in Sri Lanka, in partnership with the Rotaract Club of Colombo North.",
        "Speaking on this donation, Seshan Gunatilaka, Country Head and Vice President of Delivery at CAKE Engineering, said, \u201cit is in moments such as these, where organizations need to play a major role in uplifting communities. With all the difficulties daily-wage earners are experiencing today, we hope that at least for a brief period, we can fulfill their most basic of needs by ensuring they are able to have three meals a day\u201d.",
        "Part of Mad Mobile Inc., CAKE Engineering is a Global Engineering Centre located in Sri Lanka, developing groundbreaking products for the global restaurant and retail industry. With an enterprise focus, and harnessing the power of Sri Lankan engineering excellence, the organization uses leading-edge technology to build solutions that changes the way industries connect with the customers and run their businesses.",
        "Share market recovers in mid-session subsequent to starting on negative note",
        "AIA Insurance wins the highly esteemed award title \u2018Digital Insurance Initiative of the Year in Sri Lanka\u2019",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
      ],
